SELECT u.id, '34460706', 'e9e3b0039f203a6af32eabf6aa58261e', '+5535998352323', NOW(), NOW()
FROM users u WHERE u.openId = (SELECT openId FROM users ORDER BY lastSignedIn DESC LIMIT 1)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE apiId = '34460706', apiHash = 'e9e3b0039f203a6af32eabf6aa58261e', phoneNumber = '+5535998352323', updatedAt = NOW();
